data.description: Discover the charm of this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence, ideally situated just a brief stroll from Sutro Elementary School. This home boasts extra space including a formal dining area, a cozy living room, and an expansive great room. The well-appointed open kitchen features a convenient breakfast bar, top-of-the-line Samsung black stainless appliances, a gas range, and a pantry. With a seamless flow into the family room, the kitchen offers captivating views of the backyard. The fully landscaped lot comes complete with automatic sprinklers, a storage shed for your convenience, and RV Parking. Indulge in the comforts of the primary ensuite, featuring dual sinks, a soaking tub, and an oversized closet. The thoughtfully designed split floorplan ensures privacy by separating the primary suite from the secondary bedrooms. Recent upgrades include a new furnace, air conditioner, and water heater, enhancing the overall efficiency and functionality of the home.
